In[8]:
for ep in range(1, n_epochs+1):
    loss_base, stats_base = train_step(
        model_base, opt_base, X0, X1, tangent_pairs, device,
        use_tangent=False, batch_size=batch_size
    )

    loss_tan, stats_tan = train_step(
        model_tan, opt_tan, X0, X1, tangent_pairs, device,
        use_tangent=True, batch_size=batch_size
    )
    if ep % 50 == 0:
        print(f"Epoch {ep:03d} | base: {loss_base} | tan: {loss_tan}")

In[11]:
t0 = t_idx.min()
idx_t0 = np.where(t_idx == t0)[0]
Z_t0 = Z[idx_t0]

# remove extreme boundary points
center = Z_t0.mean(axis=0)
dist = np.linalg.norm(Z_t0 - center, axis=1)
keep = dist < np.percentile(dist, 80)   # keep core 80%

n_seeds = 30
seed_idx = np.random.choice(idx_t0[keep], size=n_seeds, replace=False)
Z_seeds = Z[seed_idx]
